We welcome proposals for papers to be included in a Special Issue of the
journal 'Themes in Science and Technology Education' on "Computer-aided
language analysis, teaching and learning: approaches, perspectives and
applications".

Themes within the scope of this special issue include:
&#8226; Applications of ICT for language analysis (e.g., corpus analysis,
readability analysis).
&#8226; Language teaching technologies (e.g., CBT, teaching delivery
systems, case
studies).
&#8226; Language learning technologies (e.g., CALL, VLEs, learning
assessment and
competence testing).

GUEST EDITORS
